  "description": "<p><strong>微软在Windows 8.1预览版发布不足一周时间的今天，刚刚通过Windows更新程序向用户推送了首批系统更新。</strong>本次共有6个系统更新，其中2个显示为“重要”级别，其他4个则为“推荐”更新。更新的内容包含了一些针对Windows Defender防护的病毒数据更新，以及Windows Store应用的补丁修复。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e27070f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243376.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%90%91Windows+8.1%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%E7%89%88%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243376.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%90%91Windows+8.1%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%E7%89%88%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243376.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%90%91Windows+8.1%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%E7%89%88%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243376.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%90%91Windows+8.1%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%E7%89%88%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243376.htm&amp