  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243375.htm", 
  "description": "<p> <strong>苹果Mac OS X系统的默认壁纸一直很好看，第一代Mac OS X使用的是Aqua桌面，随后10.2 Jaguar，10.3 Panther以及10.4 Tiger都对原始的Aqua抽象桌面壁纸进行了改变，使这张Aqua壁纸看起来更现代，细节更多。</strong>在Mac OS X 10.5 Leopard发布后，苹果选择了不同风格的默认壁纸，也就是我们所熟知的星空壁纸，在OS X 10.6 Snow Leopard、10.7 Lion和10.8 Mountain Lion中使用的全是星空壁纸。 </p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e27070e/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243375.htm&amp;t=%E5%90%84%E4%BB%A3OS+X%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%A3%81%E7%BA%B8%E6%AC%A3%E8%B5%8F%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%8E%E6%8A%BD%E8%B1%A1%E5%88%B0%E6%98%9F%E7%A9%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%B7%A8%E6%B5%AA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243375.htm&amp;t=%E5%90%84%E4%BB%A3OS+X%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%A3%81%E7%BA%B8%E6%AC%A3%E8%B5%8F%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%8E%E6%8A%BD%E8%B1%A1%E5%88%B0%E6%98%9F%E7%A9%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%B7%A8%E6%B5%AA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243375.htm&amp;t=%E5%90%84%E4%BB%A3OS+X%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%A3%81%E7%BA%B8%E6%AC%A3%E8%B5%8F%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%8E%E6%8A%BD%E8%B1%A1%E5%88%B0%E6%98%9F%E7%A9%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%B7%A8%E6%B5%AA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243375.htm&amp;t=%E5%90%84%E4%BB%A3OS+X%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%A3%81%E7%BA%B8%E6%AC%A3%E8%B5%8F%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%8E%E6%8A%BD%E8%B1%A1%E5%88%B0%E6%98%9F%E7%A9%BA%EF%