  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243374.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>感谢<a href=\"http://www.ofgeek.com\" target=\"_blank\">ofGEEK</a>的投递</strong><br /></p><p>有时候因为工作需要或其他原因，我们会将手机调为振动，而手机振动则意味着有新提醒（包括微信和微博回复、电子邮件、短信、电话等），你曾经多少次将手机从口袋里取出查看呢？研究发现，八成应答为错觉。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e27070d/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243374.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%B8%B8%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%A3%E8%A2%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%8C%AF%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%A7%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243374.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%B8%B8%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%A3%E8%A2%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%8C%AF%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%A7%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243374.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%B8%B8%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%A3%E8%A2%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%8C%AF%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%A7%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243374.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%B8%B8%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%A3%E8%A2%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%8C%AF%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%A7%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%