  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243373.htm", 
  "description": "<p>微软先前在Windows 8中就为触控板加入了一些手势操作，不过笔记本触控板的所有优势也并未因此全部发挥出来。<strong>在Windows 8.1系统中，微软显然更加注重此问题，并且同合作伙伴更亲密地联系期望可以提升Windows系统的使用体验。</strong>在近期举行的Build大会 上，Windows项目经理James Clarke就列举了相关触控板方面，8.1系统的部分改进。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e27070b/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243373.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8EIntel%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87Win8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%8B%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7%E6%9D%BF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243373.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8EIntel%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87Win8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%8B%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7%E6%9D%BF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243373.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8EIntel%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87Win8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%8B%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7%E6%9D%BF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243373.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8EIntel%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87Win8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%8B%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7%E6%9D%BF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http